---
title: Spooky Chicken Stir-Fry
description: We’ve whipped up some scarily good food at the HelloFresh Farm to treat you this Halloween! Don’t let our ghoulish white and black peppers give you a fright! They get their hue from phytonutrients like anthocyanin and beta-carotene which have great health benefits. We hope this scrumptious stir-fry gets you into the spooky spirit!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/spooky-chicken-stir-fry-wk44-f5e97d3e.jpg
